Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡…惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙的武力介入這是第七次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管三七二十一地攻擊軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且將對方全部殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不是阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也聽到世界的惡意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密那邊的聯絡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們待機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.93,0:01:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這邊的計劃全都泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐那邊  計劃變更也快完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Gundam該做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是義大利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動攻擊的果然是那三台新型Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統  那些新型號的武力介入的內容和以前的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為聯合演習觸到了Gundam的逆鱗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠我們的話已經無法和Celestial Being對抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請批准加強和聯合及人革聯的配合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能打倒Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無對策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  Gundam會對這裡發動攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們的目的是毀滅世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道新型的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連作為監視者的你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有在吠陀設定的權限等級內的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的小隊名字叫三位一體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱的MS是Gundam Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的就這麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是個人意見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得作戰行動似乎越來越過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為三位一體的存在也是本計劃的一部分嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這種意見比較妥當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  他們都是擁有名為Gundam的機體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種叫Throne的機體  系統和裝甲用的都是和我們同樣的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是同型機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是GN Drive不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同是指…太陽爐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機能上是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爐心部分沒使用TD Planted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drive本身的活動時間有限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話  這應該算擬似太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人從Celestial Being偷取技術  建造了Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐的設計資料只有吠陀中才有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人侵入了吠陀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世事無絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假使是這樣  要建造太陽爐也需要大量的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少能肯定組織中有叛徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 3  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 4  Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7的領域內的資料  一部分被改動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個資料領域到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:48.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然不能訪問…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.39,0:05:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼  吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果世界認為三位一體是我們的同伴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在繼續任務就很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據情況儘量收集他們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再考慮對策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全看王留美的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐  關於普特利麥奧斯傳來的三位一體的身體資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現有一致的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續調查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體的做法確實很魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果這樣能使世界改變的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍華德·梅森
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙非常尊敬隊長您的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來駕駛被選定為次期主力MS的Flag
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是多虧了作為測試飛行員的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是確信Flag的性能是最高的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才當測試飛行員的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  在性能試驗中的模擬戰還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不幸的事故  隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  這傢伙這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「多虧了隊長  我才能成為Flag Fighter」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這樣一來就能和隊長一起在天上飛了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  他比我還要愛Flag啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我向霍華德·梅森發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  格拉哈姆·艾卡  要駕駛Flag擊敗Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}聯合  美國南部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  特地把你叫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總比在軍隊附近見面要好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  酬金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塔克拉瑪干沙漠的聯合軍事演習裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎目睹了新型Gundam對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然聽到了駕駛員的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對話？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我乘坐的Realdo被Gundam擊落了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等待救援的時候看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  向拉古娜報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然隔著頭盔看不到臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從體型和聲音來看  駕駛員是年輕女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對話裡是說「向拉古娜報告」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我所知道的就這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事有沒有向軍方…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:56.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我估計會有像你這樣的人高價來買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事能暫時不對任何人講嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得提高酬金才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在近日內把現金送到你那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來女兒的生日party就能開得比較華麗點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「向拉古娜報告」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「拉古娜」是什麼的名字？還是暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來值得調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我也在追求事實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且把這些結合起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  找出真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:49.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}AEU  西班牙北部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們倆幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  哈萊維夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨  沙慈  還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換班太多都累得精疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜也不錯  還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離目標金額還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  送貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎麼搞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光  難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害  第一次親眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古娜傳來下一個任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  最近出動太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成戰爭根絕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這邊拼命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊還玩得那麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界正在改變哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個不是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:12:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…  媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  按錯鍵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連續作戰累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許隨便行動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體對平民進行攻擊到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是針對助長紛爭的異端分子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個似乎不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吠陀裡的三位一體的任務資料裡也沒有記載
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無意義的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧著玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對平民的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是恐怖襲擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是MS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所撥打的電話號碼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了  被她父母阻止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國際留學生路易絲·哈萊維嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  已經三天沒來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯  算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萊維小姐好像在故鄉西班牙遇到事故入院了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事故是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體的情況不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經發出休學申請了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我醫院的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西班牙的修養地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據生存者的證詞證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次災難是Gundam的攻擊造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}聯合  美國  伊利諾伊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這個時間還來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該還在住院…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的話  這台Flag特裝型的整備就做不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說也是埃夫曼教授親自調整過的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你有不會妥協的事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有不會妥協的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠要強的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:15:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Flags的總部被Gundam襲擊的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是埃夫曼教授
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授正在接近Gundam的能源機構和特殊粒子的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知用什麼方法知道此事的Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以武力介入為掩護  抹殺了教授
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊裡有通風報信的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為沒有的話就不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛荷華上空F3988點發現疑為Gundam的機影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地點的設施的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲公司的軍需工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是軍需工廠  工作的可是平民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  Flag能出動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉哈姆機  先出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然單獨出擊  太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種道理  就用我的無理來撬開！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}聯合  美國  愛麗絲公司工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個速度是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣程度的性能差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.94,0:16:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是淩駕於阿修羅之上的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報了一箭之仇了  霍華德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體承受不了這種程度的重力嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體那些傢伙又在亂搞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊了愛麗絲公司的兵器工廠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有800多人死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,員工都是平民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟無差別恐怖襲擊沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為本計劃的生命線的量子型演算處理系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼人能侵入吠陀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將不得不放棄使用吠陀繼續實行計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比利發來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃夫曼教授過世了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由於Gundam的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲受傷…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是到西班牙去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂跑很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你遇到了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  來得晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃學了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  太好了  你很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不是慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是以前路易絲想要的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.23,0:19:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考完放假那段時間努力打工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於買來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.55,0:19:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  對路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對路易絲你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是好不容易才買來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我戴不上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴不上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲小姐的雙親和親屬都在事故中死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別刺激她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管它根除戰爭還是什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打仗的話就有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再怎麼拼命治療傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也治不了心理創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈萊維家就是那個有名的資產家？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是被Gundam襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.39,0:20:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後跟戰爭有牽連嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們是平民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作馬上又要增加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有讓大哥手忙腳亂的傢伙在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽是大敵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能銘記在心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.20,0:21:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種粒子光束是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  目標捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三部Gundam Throne判定為輔助紛爭的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:18.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:24.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:33.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:41.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:46.78,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:47.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:53.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:58.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:12.83,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:18.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:23.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:30.82,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:18.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有著相同的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:24.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那樣的我們也已過了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交錯的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:33.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無法接受並急躁著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:41.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}捨棄了無用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:46.78,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}給予這世界以溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.92,0:22:47.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:53.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便顯示出勇氣　即便逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:58.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一個人亦是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.61,0:23:02.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.70,0:23:07.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心靈深處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:12.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延續...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:18.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由於不可忘記　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:23.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要離去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:30.82,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還要留在這廣闊大地同伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇的對象就在自己身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得知這一事實的洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以衝動的感情舉起了槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「羈絆」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.28,0:23:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊的目標  會是…


